    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-coral text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-coral/90 transition-colors">
        Read the Blog
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joewegner/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-white/30 text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:border-coral hover:text-coral transition-colors">
        LinkedIn
